# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Mutual Fund FAQ Assistant (Facts-Only RAG) — environment variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Setup:
#   1. Copy this file to ".env"  ->  cp .env.example .env
#   2. Paste your Groq API key below.
#   3. Never commit ".env" (it is gitignored).
#
# This project needs exactly ONE secret. Embeddings run locally via the BGE
# model (sentence-transformers) — no embeddings API key is required; the model
# downloads automatically on first run.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Groq API key — powers BOTH the intent/refusal gate (llama-3.1-8b-instant)
# and the facts-only generator (llama-3.3-70b-versatile).
# Get one (free tier available) at: https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=
